name: Demon Dude #1
description: Demon Dudes are a limited collectible set of 33 different demons. Each will cost 3 Tezos with 33 Editions. The final very SPECIAL Demon Dude will be released March 3 2022 and cost 333 Tezos and only 1 will be Available.Inspired by my first NFT ever created under the same name. If you collect 3 Demon Dudes you will get a free bonus NFT only available to people who own 3 Demon Dudes. Inventory won’t last long
